des: KQEN continues to step up their programming with local morning, afternoon, and evening news. Inside Douglas County with Kyle Bailey interviews local politicians, teachers, and other community leaders. KQEN also features strong talk programs featuring Rush Limbaugh, Dave Ramsey, Lars Larson, and Coast to Coast along with local talk Monday through Friday 4:00 PM - 5:00 PM. KQEN also broadcasts University of Oregon sports!
